'<!-- Recursive multiline definition of the [Fibonacci](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fibonacci_number) function $fib(n)$, illustrating self-referential calls and conditional base cases. -->
'Function:
fib(n) = if(n ≡ 1; 1;
  $block{
    a = 0;
    b = 1;
    $repeat{
       c = a + b;
       a ← b;
       b ← c;
     @ k = 1 : n - 1} _
  } _
)
'Results:
#for i = 1 : 9
	fib(i)
#loop
